{"id":"93649351-76f1-41b2-b3bf-3dbbd7f22f65","timestamp":"2026-05-20T23:14:06.350Z","type":"gemini","content":"To set up Jan to use Ollama and its models, follow these steps:\n\n### 1. Verify Ollama is Running\nEnsure the Ollama service is active. On your system, it is already running (PID 33901). You can confirm by visiting `http://localhost:11434` in your browser or running:\n```bash\nollama list\n```\n*Current models available on your system include `llama3.1:8b-instruct-q4_K_M` and `llama3:8b-instruct-q4_K_M`.*\n\n### 2. Enable the Ollama Extension in Jan\n1. Open the **Jan AI** application.\n2. Click the **Settings** (gear icon) in the bottom-left corner.\n3. Navigate to the **Extensions** tab in the sidebar.\n4. Locate the **Ollama** extension and click **Enable**. \n\n### 3. Configure the Connection\n1. Once enabled, click on the **Ollama extension settings** (usually a gear or \"Settings\" button next to the extension).\n2. Ensure the **Server URL** is set to: `http://localhost:11434`.\n3. Save the settings.\n\n### 4. Select and Use Models\n1. Go to the **Hub** or **Models** section in Jan.\n2. Your local Ollama models (e.g., `llama3.1:8b-instruct-q4_K_M`) should now appear in the list.\n3. Click **Use** or **Select** on the model you wish to chat with.\n\n### Manual Setup (If Extension is Unavailable)\nIf you cannot find the Ollama extension, you can add it as an OpenAI-compatible provider:\n1. Go to **Settings** > **Model Providers**.\n2. Select **OpenAI** (or Add Provider).\n3. Set **Base URL** to `http://localhost:11434/v1`.\n4. Set **API Key** to `ollama` (any value works, but it's required).\n5. Add your models manually by entering their exact name from `ollama list` (e.g., `llama3.1:8b-instruct-q4_K_M`).","thoughts":[{"subject":"Confirming Ollama Access","description":"I've verified Ollama is active and accessible. My focus has shifted to confirming the necessary configurations for Jan to integrate seamlessly with it, ensuring all parameters are correctly set.","timestamp":"2026-05-20T23:14:03.541Z"}],"tokens":{"input":22612,"output":497,"cached":18867,"thoughts":159,"tool":0,"total":23268},"model":"gemini-3-flash-preview"}
