o add the package. Once identified, I will update both `flake.nix` and the configuration to include the new tool.\n\nStrategic Intent: Updating system to include the new Antigravity CLI via Nix flake."}}}],"status":"success","timestamp":"2026-05-21T01:44:10.602Z","resultDisplay":"## 📂 Topic: **Installing Antigravity CLI**\n\n**Summary:**\nThe user wants to proceed with installing Antigravity CLI by adding it to their NixOS flake. I am now reading `nixos/configuration.nix` to find the appropriate place to add the package. Once identified, I will update both `flake.nix` and the configuration to include the new tool.\n\n> [!STRATEGY]\n> **Intent:** Updating system to include the new Antigravity CLI via Nix flake.","description":"Update topic to: \"Installing Antigravity CLI\"","displayName":"Update Topic Context","renderOutputAsMarkdown":true},{"id":"read_file_1779327850377_1","name":"read_file","args":{"file_path":"/home/nondeus/.nix-config/nixos/configuration.nix"},"result":[{"functionResponse":{"id":"read_file_1779327850377_1","name":"read_file","response":{"output":"{ config, pkgs, inputs, lib, ... }: {\n\n  imports = [\n    ./vms.nix\n  ];\n\n\n\n  # Kernel & Performance\n  boot = {\n    initrd.systemd.enable = true;\n    kernelModules = [ \"amdgpu\" \"nvidia\" \"nvidia_modeset\" \"nvidia_uvm\" \"nvidia_drm\" ];\n    kernelParams = [\n      \"nvidia-drm.modeset=1\"\n      \"nvidia.NVreg_EnableGpuFirmware=1\"\n      \"nvidia.NVreg_PreserveVideoMemoryAllocations=1\"\n      \"preempt=full\"\n      \"threadirqs\"\n    ];\n    kernelPackages = pkgs.cachyosKernels.linuxPackages-cachyos-latest;\n    kernel.sysctl = {\n      # Memory Management\n      \"vm.max_map_count\" = 2147483642;\n      \"vm.swappiness\" = 180;\n      \"vm.page-cluster\" = 0;\n      \"vm.vfs_cache_pressure\" = 50;\n      # Scheduling\n      \"kernel.sched_cfs_bandwidth_slice_us\" = 3000;\n      # Network\n      \"net.core.netdev_max_backlog\" = 16384;\n      \"net.core.somaxconn\" = 8192;\n      \"n