{"id":"c100005e-d37f-4615-9516-fd24f532ff2f","timestamp":"2026-05-21T03:12:08.067Z","type":"user","content":[{"text":"so i rebuilt with no errors, and then jan decided to freeze the entire system, i think i was attempting to use a model that required more vram than i have, so the antigravity binary was not downloaded with the nix rebuild automatically?"}]}
